    {"field":"experienceFoundation","match":"可以让游客动手参与","effects":{"experience":16,"course":6,"scene":6},"reason":"游客可参与度高，适合设计收费体验或研学环节。","factorType":"positive"},
    {"field":"experienceFoundation","match":"适合 15-30 分钟轻体验","effects":{"experience":11,"operation":7,"scene":5},"reason":"短时体验更适合景区、街区和市集快速周转。","factorType":"positive"},
    {"field":"experienceFoundation","match":"适合 30-60 分钟标准体验","effects":{"experience":13,"course":5,"operation":4},"reason":"标准体验时长适合形成可售体验单元。","factorType":"positive"},
    {"field":"experienceFoundation","match":"适合 60-90 分钟深度体验","effects":{"experience":10,"course":10,"operation":-2},"reason":"深度体验适合预约制课程，但普通散客转化门槛较高。","factorType":"positive"},
